<paragraph id="E42B180A51B918D4FF0EF8EEEE5C1BB1" blockId="130.[151,1437,1905,2038]" pageId="130" pageNumber="131">
<emphasis id="D6E0C41851B918D4FF0EF8EEEE491BCD" bold="true" box="[151,369,1905,1930]" pageId="130" pageNumber="131">FIGURES 394−404.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="2394638951B918D4FEE2F8EEED601BCE" authorityName="Ho" authorityYear="2019" baseAuthorityName="Olivier" baseAuthorityYear="1883" box="[379,600,1905,1929]" class="Insecta" family="Lampyridae" genus="Pygoluciola" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="130" pageNumber="131" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="insularis" status="comb. nov.">
<emphasis id="D6E0C41851B918D4FEE2F8EEED601BCE" box="[379,600,1905,1929]" italics="true" pageId="130" pageNumber="131">Pygoluciola insularis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis id="D6E0C41851B918D4FDF8F8EEEDE01BCE" bold="true" box="[609,728,1905,1929]" pageId="130" pageNumber="131">
<taxonomicNameLabel id="CDD3796351B918D4FDF8F8EEEDE01BCE" box="[609,728,1905,1929]" pageId="130" pageNumber="131" rank="species">comb. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
394, 395, 400 type female (MNHN); 396−399, 401−404 Andaman Islands males (NHML). 394, 397 habitus ventral; 395, 396 habitus dorsal; 398, 399 abdomen: 398 ventral; 399 dorsal; 400 type label; 401 aedeagal sheath ventral; 402−403 aedeagus: 402 ventral; 403 dorsal; 404 tergite 8 ventral with aedeagal sheath and aedeagus contained.
</paragraph>
